snippet.title: TrinityS - Gameplay / (PC)
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1584690/TrinityS/
TrintyS condenses the thrilling elements of MMO RPG endgame encounters into a white-knuckle, "Boss Rush" cooperative online action game for up to three players. Skip the MMO level grind and face off against fearsome foes that require precise coordination to defeat!
